day/how-to-destroy-the-business-model-of-breitbart-and-fake-news.html|title=How to Destroy the Business Model of Breitbart and Fake News |last=Kennedy|first=Pagan|date=January 7, 2017|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|accessdate=January 10, 2017}}</ref><ref name=":11">{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/dec/08/breitbart-looks-to-france-and-germany-another-alt-right-victory-steve-bannon|title=German firms including BMW pull advertising from Breitbart|last=Henley|first=Jon|date=December 8, 2016 |last2=Oltermann |first2=Philip|newspaper=[[The Guardian]]|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077|accessdate=January 5, 2017}}</ref><ref name="auto3">{{cite web |url=http://www.valuewalk.com/2017/05/amazon-drop-breitbart/|title=Coalition Gather More Than One Million Petition Signatures Urging Amazon To Drop Breitbart|last=|first=|date=May 8, 2017|website=ValueWalk|access-date=}}</ref>

